column6: I love all of my lululemon pieces, but for some reason these had an unusual fit. I wear the same size pants across most of lululemon and never have problems. I was super excited about these but the crotch and knees felt oddly tight. Very cute, just bummed they didn't fit quite right.

column6: My profession as a sports and orthopedic physical therapist requires that I move, demonstrate exercise, and have down time to fit in a work out. These leggings are stylish yet incredibly functional and allow me to go from my work flow to my workout session. Love them!
Poor fit. Not the usual... can I return?

column6:
While These are super cute and flattering on, I don’t see how I’m going to be able to work out in them. The waistband has been rolling down repeatedly, as the fabric is super thin with zero compression. I have similar pants in emerald, and they are perfection. I can’t stop tugging on these, and i Haven’t even started my workout.
These would be great for casual wear as they are great looking pants; however, I will not be wearing them for workouts after today.

column6: I love these tights! They look amazing and feel amazing. Super slimming and comfortable enough to be worn all day long. I need 15 more pairs of these!
Very flattering and fun! I would recoomend to all my friends. True to normal lululemon sizing.
Great fit! Very comfortable. Already lots of complements!

Nothing wrong with the quality, but the fit wasn't quite what I wanted. It was actually quite baggy in places, especially around the ankles, which was unflattering. I don't know if it was the cut or style or if I just have short legs.
Not only this design looks great also very comfortable. I highly recommende it.

I have been a fan of Lululemon since they first opened here in Honolulu. They always kept me dry and comfortable even during intense workouts. I have tried many other brands and nothing compares but lately their new tights have been disappointingly itchy at the seams. Yes I have returned all four of the tights and am still waiting for my refund.

column5: The color I got was sheer in the butt
column6: Hi Lululemon, I bought these in white and I just put these on and was about to pull off the tag but decided to do one last check for sheerness when I was informed by a loved one that they are see through in the butt. There's NO way I can wear these to class! And I was really looking forward to it :( I would have been so embarrassed! I was also hoping to buy a new color since I liked these so much but now I'm a little hesitant. I am VERY disappointed!! :( Now I'm stuck with a pair of leggings, still with tags on, that I won't be able to wear anywhere.
column15: white colorway was sheer on me

column6:
I wore these out over the weekend with a pair of suntan pantyhose underneath with some black heels paired with a sheer black blouse. I got SO MANY compliments on them. I love the way they looked with the pantyhose underneath.
I will say the leggings would slide down a bit when I was dancing but maybe it could've been the pantyhose (thank god I was wearing hip pads to help keep them up)!
Thanks for making these!
Xoxo,
Christina aka Tom
column15: a little slippery with the pantyhose

column6:
I love the design and quality of the pants.
I wore them to an amusement park and got so many compliments!
However, the pants don’t stay still.
I had to pull them up a lot of times :(
I really want to love them but they’re not as perfect as I would like them to be.

column6:
TDLR; Do not purchase, if you are a woman with thick legs that rub together.
While the purchase of pants were absolutely "workout worthy" they did not meet my expectations. Due to the different materials sewing, which drew me to purchase, they ended being too tight and made my skin bulge at the seams between materials. Overall not impressed by this product or quality of the seams, but I know Lulu will do better next time.
I got these leggings last week and they are a little bit itchy. But I think once I give them a wash they will be ok! They are so gorgeous though!! They are fitted as well so it’s like a legging hug!

The details are perfect on these. I’d say if you are between sizes, size up because the mesh paneling stretches a little less. Lulu—please make more leggings with details and mesh paneling! They are SO cute and bring another element of confidence to my workouts.

I love these tights! The color is so pretty and I love how the mesh goes all around and not just in the back like the other ones. The quality is really good and i feel like it will last a life time. It also hug in all the right places. Plus side, it makes my butt look good :)
